        "synopsis": {
            "value": "While on a trip to Bingchuan, medical student Lin Mo Bai gets into a serious accident. To save him, his scientist father gives him mechanical enhancements. Lin Mo Bai becomes half-human and half-robot. When he and journalism intern Jiang Meng accidentally meet, she falls in love at first sight. That encounter inspires a one-sided pursuit to win his heart. How will a half-human, half-robot with artificial intelligence navigate romance, family and friendship?",
